\c 2
\p
\v 1 Kwakulosuku futhi lapho amadodana kaNkulunkulu afika ukuzimisa phambi kweN\nd kosi\nd*, uSathane laye wafika phakathi kwawo ukuzimisa phambi kweN\nd kosi\nd*.
\v 2 IN\nd kosi\nd* yasisithi kuSathane: Uvela ngaphi? USathane wasephendula iN\nd kosi\nd* wathi: Ekuzulazuleni emhlabeni lekuhambahambeni kuwo.
\v 3 IN\nd kosi\nd* yasisithi kuSathane: Ubekile yini inhliziyo yakho encekwini yami uJobe? Ngoba kakho onjengaye emhlabeni, umuntu opheleleyo loqondileyo, owesaba uNkulunkulu, loxwaya ububi? Usabambelele kubo ubuqotho bakhe, lanxa ungivuse ukuze ngimchithe\f + \fk ukuchitha: \fl Heb. \fq ukuginya.\f* kungelasizatho.
\v 4 USathane wasephendula iN\nd kosi\nd* wathi: Isikhumba ngesikhumba, yebo, konke umuntu alakho uzakunikelela impilo yakhe.
\v 5 Kodwa khathesi yelula isandla sakho, uthinte ithambo lakhe lenyama yakhe\x + 1.11.\x*; isibili uzakuthuka\f + \fk ukuthuka: \fl Heb. \fq ukubusisa.\f* ebusweni bakho\x + 1.5.\x*.
\v 6 IN\nd kosi\nd* yasisithi kuSathane: Khangela, usesandleni sakho; kodwa gcina impilo yakhe\x + 1.12.\x*.
\p
\v 7 USathane wasephuma phambi kweN\nd kosi\nd*, wamtshaya uJobe ngamathumba amabi\x + Levi 13.18.\x*, kusukela ngaphansi konyawo lwakhe kuze kube enkanda yakhe\x + 7.3,5,13-15. 13.14,28. 16.8,15. 17.1. 19.17,20. 30.17,18,30. Dute. 28.35.Isa. 1.6.\x*.
\v 8 Wasezithathela udengezi ukuziphala ngalo, wahlala phakathi kwesilotha\x + 42.6. Hez. 27.30. Jona 3.6. Mat. 11.21. Esta 4.1.\x*.
\p
\v 9 Umkakhe wasesithi kuye: Usabambelele yini\x + 21.15. 2 Kho. 6.33.\x* kubuqotho bakho\x + 2.3. 2 Sam. 6.20.\x*? Thuka uNkulunkulu, ufe\x + 1.5.\x*.
\v 10 Kodwa wathi kuye: Ukhuluma njengokukhuluma komunye wabesifazana abayiziwula\x + 2 Sam. 13.13. Hlu. 19.23.\x*. Kambe, sizakwemukela okuhle kuNkulunkulu, singemukeli lokubi yini\x + Jak. 5.10,11.\x*? Kukho konke lokhu\x + 1.22.\x* uJobe konanga ngendebe zakhe\x + Hlab. 39.1.\x*.
\p
\v 11 Abangane abathathu bakaJobe sebezwile ngakho konke lokhu okubi okumehleleyo, beza, lowo lalowo evela endaweni yakhe, uElifazi umThemani\x + 1 Lan. 1.45.\x*, loBilidadi umShuhi\x + Gen. 25.2. 1 Lan. 1.32.\x*, loZofari umNahama; bavumelana ndawonye\x + Neh. 6.2.\x* ukuthi beze bamkhalele bamduduze\x + 42.11. Isa. 51.19.\x*.
\v 12 Lapho bephakamisa amehlo abo bekhatshana, kabamazanga, baphakamisa ilizwi labo, bakhala inyembezi, badabula ngulowo ibhatshi lakhe\x + Gen. 44.13.\x*, bavuvuzela uthuli emakhanda abo ngasemazulwini\x + Josh. 7.6.\x*.
\v 13 Basebehlala laye emhlabathini insuku eziyisikhombisa lobusuku obuyisikhombisa, njalo kakho owakhuluma ilizwi kuye, ngoba babona ukuthi ubuhlungu bukhulu kakhulu\x + Hez. 3.15. Gen. 50.10.\x*.